summary: Two lovely presets for you to enjoy whilst I decide what I'm going to do.
descriptionHtml:
Pretty much both ladies use the same mods that you will need for the presets to work. I have also included the dds. and nif. facegen files. 

You will need:
12femalebrows: This is included in the Fair Skin mod.
SG Hair 350: Can be easily found via the wide web.
Miken Eyes: here on Nexus.
I use UUNP FairSkin textures.
Also, I use makeup tweaks so your results may not
match mine.
author: Kittyness
